file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test

components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        type: string
    Bar:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
    Baz:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        type: array
        items:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Bar"
    Quak:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        oneof:
          - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
          - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Bar"
